beer.beer_name: Who Is Your Daddy And What Does He Brew?
beer.beer_description: ‘Triple Dry Hopped using Experimental New Zealand Hop, NZH-107, with its bold Guava, Passion Fruit and Citrus character, and a blend of two yeast strains producing big tropical fruit flavours throughout fermentation, it’s no surprise the end result here is a complete kaleidoscopic fruit bomb’
